{"tid":1798892,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"其實如果係張華峰害死自己個女，警察有心包庇我哋都唔會知架喎","createTime":"2019-12-26T14:29:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-26T19:22:54.000Z","uid":67356,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"78f3bb2726a337d6740219988d135a53a8a90445","tid":1798892,"uid":67356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T14:29:19.000Z","msg":"大可以查都唔洗查，直接咪話佢情緒病自殺囉<br />\n佢係咪真係有病、背後咩事導致情緒病、患病後屋企人點樣對佢...其實呢啲都可以成為一個人「自殺」嘅原因<br />\n講真，情緒病自殺係病逝，需要大家同情<br />\n但如果係屋企人逼死病人，咁同謀殺真係冇分別囉<br />\n<br />\n而我係唔信警察會對<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">監警會副主席張華峰太平紳士</span></strong>作出公正全面嘅調查囉"},{"pid":"069a856043c52015f588b308035e02661d0d0dba","tid":1798892,"uid":50740,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T15:22:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tnYKeWt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtnYKeWt.jpg&h=0f34dcbf&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"86960b4c6883875aa77b3abfb8bc42308ed5494f","tid":1798892,"uid":67356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T15:42:08.000Z","msg":"rip<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0587db8e6b4d8c199046fb992a71cb4c6b4d4786","tid":1798892,"uid":185121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T17:30:38.000Z","msg":"佢屋企人其實好可疑囉<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/StopTortureHK/photos/a.737784732942710/2583247145063117/?type=3&amp;source=57\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2FStopTortureHK%2Fphotos%2Fa.737784732942710%2F2583247145063117%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26source%3D57&d=xSG8yb8yy9PjQoJ4RYEJZEVeFFKYYtZMgzuY3n553xQ%3D&h=04007160\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/StopTortureHK/photos/a.737784732942710/2583247145063117/?type=3&amp;source=57</a>"},{"pid":"d2460670edda40bd6d63de168173f06cf2b6603f","tid":1798892,"uid":307619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T19:22:54.000